?panx-framework v0.1.2
-------------------

?This is next release of panx-framework (v0.1.2).

?The documentation is available on https://panx.eu/docs/
!(In future, it will available only using https://panx.eu/docs/v0.1.2/)

?New features
- Fixed bugs
- Added Request class
- Clean install without specifing the version
- Update command - You can now pass a version (Fix)
- Auto language
- Added comments to /app/classes/

?After installation
After installation, you need to run following commands:
?composer install
?php panx-worker config